            <title><![CDATA[【图集】人大闭幕会 习近平等按键投票]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[<div class="figure-media figure-media-gallery figure-media-gallery-overlay js-figure-media-gallery js-figure-media-gallery-overlay"> <div class="figure-media-gallery-slide"><div class="figure-media-gallery-img"><img class="lazyload" data-src="https://www.zaobao.com.sg/sites/default/files/styles/article_large_full/public/images/202103/20210311/a2.jpg?itok=EH6pQudG" alt data-caption="中国国家主席习近平（左）与国务院总理李克强按下桌上的按钮投票。（法新社）" src="https://www.zaobao.com.sg/sites/default/files/styles/article_large_full/public/images/202103/20210311/a2.jpg?itok=EH6pQudG" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><div class="tint"></div></div><figcaption><p>中国国家主席习近平（左）与国务院总理李克强按下桌上的按钮投票。（法新社）</p></figcaption></div> <div class="figure-media-gallery-slide"><div class="figure-media-gallery-img"><img class="lazyload" data-src="https://www.zaobao.com.sg/sites/default/files/styles/article_large_full/public/images/202103/20210311/a3.jpg?itok=ELSoDzKP" alt data-caption="中国国家主席习近平按键投票。从图中可见，有绿红黄三种颜色的按钮。（法新社）" src="https://www.zaobao.com.sg/sites/default/files/styles/article_large_full/public/images/202103/20210311/a3.jpg?itok=ELSoDzKP" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><div class="tint"></div></div><figcaption><p>中国国家主席习近平按键投票。从图中可见，有绿红黄三种颜色的按钮。（法新社）</p></figcaption></div> <div class="figure-media-gallery-slide"><div class="figure-media-gallery-img"><img class="lazyload" data-src="https://www.zaobao.com.sg/sites/default/files/styles/article_large_full/public/images/202103/20210311/r3.jpg?itok=LQUP_cnf" alt data-caption="习近平（左）与李克强起身时交流。（路透社）" src="https://www.zaobao.com.sg/sites/default/files/styles/article_large_full/public/images/202103/20210311/r3.jpg?itok=LQUP_cnf" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><div class="tint"></div></div><figcaption><p>习近平（左）与李克强起身时交流。（路透社）</p></figcaption></div> <div class="figure-media-gallery-slide"><div class="figure-media-gallery-img"><img class="lazyload" data-src="https://www.zaobao.com.sg/sites/default/files/styles/article_large_full/public/images/202103/20210311/r2.jpg?itok=dbIVyuxX" alt data-caption="中国国家主席习近平（右）与全国政协主席汪洋在会上交流。（路透社）" src="https://www.zaobao.com.sg/sites/default/files/styles/article_large_full/public/images/202103/20210311/r2.jpg?itok=dbIVyuxX" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><div class="tint"></div></div><figcaption><p>中国国家主席习近平（右）与全国政协主席汪洋在会上交流。（路透社）</p></figcaption></div> <div class="figure-media-gallery-slide"><div class="figure-media-gallery-img"><img class="lazyload" data-src="https://www.zaobao.com.sg/sites/default/files/styles/article_large_full/public/images/202103/20210311/r1.jpg?itok=Zg-qc7J7" alt data-caption="会议结束后，习近平（中）起身准备离开会场。（路透社）" src="https://www.zaobao.com.sg/sites/default/files/styles/article_large_full/public/images/202103/20210311/r1.jpg?itok=Zg-qc7J7" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><div class="tint"></div></div><figcaption><p>会议结束后，习近平（中）起身准备离开会场。（路透社）</p></figcaption></div><div class="figure-media-gallery-nav"></div></div>

<p>中国十三届全国人大四次会议今天举行闭幕会，表决通过了包括《全国人民代表大会关于完善香港特别行政区选举制度的决定（草案）》在内的决定和报告。</p>

<p>习近平、李克强等出席会议并投票。<br>
 </p>
